text: Oldenzaal is a municipality and city in the province of Overijssel, the Netherlands. About 32,000 people were living there in 2021. It lies in Twente region. Oldenzaal got city rights in 1249. == People == * Gert Timmerman (1935-2017), a singer and musician ("Gert and Hermien") == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Cities in Overijssel Category:Municipalities of Overijssel Category:Twente
